My pieces are largely developed and I thought my opponent was in a cramped position so started moving forward with aggression

7. ... Nxd5 8. exd5 Nb4 9. a3 traps the Knight. 7. ... Nxd5 8. exd5 Na5 9. a3 b5 10. b4 Nb7 and the Knight escapes. White can also capture with the Bishop. 7. ... Nxd5 8. Bxd5 Nb4 is pretty good for black I think
